  <brief_title>Emergence Agitation in Adult Patients After Intracranial Surgery</brief_title>
  <official_title>Emergence Agitation During Recovery From Intracranial Surgery Under General Anesthesia: a Prospective Multicenter Cohort Study</official_title>
  <sponsors>
